<br />

<br />
But if you are looking at em get the 75dd aug from EF its all of 100pts. cheap enough to almost be loose change if youre considering the higher ones at all. To be honest unless you have a weapon thats cost you a fortune and youre gonna be keeping forever id look at the low end augs. And even in this case odds are you can buy the 100pt one and destroy it latter when you want to replace it. Face it if you're looking at the 1k augs you can afford to loose a hundred or so while youre saving up. And if you have the k go for armour anyway first</span></td>
